(sum zipwith should be elementwise sum) {[5 3 2] [8 3 1] {add} 2 zipwith} [[13 6 3]] assert-stack
(pair zipwith should be elementwise pair) {[5 3 2] [8 3 1] {2 array astore} 2 zipwith} [[[5 8] [3 3] [2 1]]] assert-stack
